    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Houston, Texas",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Dec. 28, 1948",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "I, [REDACTED] residing",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Houston 17, Texas make the following statement to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] and [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "representatives of the Office of Special Investigation,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Ellington OSI Detachment, Ellington Field, Texas, and b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Special Agents [REDACTED] and [REDACTED] who",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "I know to be Special Agents of the Federal Bureau of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Investigation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "On Monday afternoon December 6, 1948, at about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "6 P.M., Mr. [REDACTED] and another man, name not recalled,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "and I had dinner at the Old Virginia Inn, Los Angeles,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "California. After dinner we went back to Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "electrical manufacturing company which he owns and operates",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "in Los Angeles, California. Mr. [REDACTED] told us about seeing",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "a flying disc and we made an appointment to leave early",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "the next morning by car, with our cameras, to go to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "location of the disc. Mr. [REDACTED] was detained at some",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "private air field so we did not leave until about 2 P.M.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "on December 7, 1948. We arrived at the scene of the b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "flying disc and took pictures of the disc which was still",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "lying around. Mr. [REDACTED] took about 10 feet of 16 mm film",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "and Mr. [REDACTED] took five or six shots with a Speed Graphic",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Camera. He noticed that the first three shots were taken",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "when the adapter on his lens was closed too much and I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "don't know if they turned out all right. Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "suggested I hold the flying disc up and rotate it around",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "and he would take my picture with my camera. After",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "taking the pictures, we patched the fence of Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "property where people had been cutting the wire to get to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "a road. We left and then drove back and had dinner at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Eaton's Inn and they took me back home to Hollywood,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "California.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "I would like to recite that I left Houston, Texas",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "11:30 A.M. on Sunday, December 5, 1948, for California by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "plane and flew to Hollywood, California on a commercial",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "plane on business matters. On arriving in Hollywood, I met",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] in Hollywood on Monday, December 6, 1948, and b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "at that time he told me about the flying disc he had located.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "He stated he had gone to Las Vegas by his personal plane",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
